Docs.param: True if the Save As dialog box will be displayed.
False when the event occurs. If the event procedure sets this argument to True, the workbook isn't saved when the procedure is finished.
Docs.summary: A Delegate type used to add an event handler for the event. The WorkbookBeforeSave event occurs before any open workbook is saved.
